    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing reliable transportation. While the mechanical components, including the engine and transmission, are in good working order and have been regularly serviced, the car does show its age. You can expect some visible exterior blemishes such as minor scratches and paint fading, along with some wear on the interior upholstery. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any hidden surprises.",
